      • separation

        protected org.apache.commons.math3.geometry.euclidean.threed.Vector3D separation(ArrayList<Agent> taggedNeighborEntities)
        Separation iterates through the tagged vehicles, examining each one. The vector to each vehicle under consideration is normalized, divided by the distance to the neighbor, and added to the steering force.
